metadata: {"compiler":{"version":"0.5.16+commit.9c3226ce"},"language":"Solidity","output":{"abi":[],"devdoc":{"details":"Wrappers over Solidity's arithmetic operations with added overflow checks. * Arithmetic operations in Solidity wrap on overflow.
